/li>\r\n                <li class=\"my-3\">6 large cloves garlic, minced or pressed</li>\r\n                <li class=\"my-3\">2 (28-ounce) cans whole tomatoes, preferably San Marzano</li>\r\n                <li class=\"my-3\">1/2 cup packed fresh basil leaves, torn or roughly-chopped</li>\r\n                <li class=\"my-3\">1 teaspoon sea salt</li>\r\n                <li class=\"my-3\">1/2 teaspoon freshly-cracked black pepper</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>");
